				// Current state:
				//   tmp = λ = (y0 - jmp_y) * inverse  (slope for P+Q)
				//   tmp2 = λ² (slope squared for P+Q)
				//   inverse = 1/(x0 - jmp_x)
				//   x0, y0 = original point P
				//   jmp_x, jmp_y = jump point Q

				// === Compute P+Q first (standard) ===
